	<h1 class="title">电影《魔兽》，它会和游戏的剧情很不一样</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/506540/small/506540.jpg?1460267534" alt="">
